h 2022, racing over five kilometres inLondon's Bushy Park helped Bell fall in love with the sport again after injury had made her step away and, for a while, give up on her Olympic dream.\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bushy_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.52629350711011e-20, \"text\": \"Bushy Park\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bushy_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bushy_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"over five kilometres\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"her step\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic dream\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old was a hugely talented junior but after heading to America to study and train, a series of physical setbacks saw her quit athletics.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hugely talented junior\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"physical setbacks\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"her quit athletics\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, after a tentative return to running during lockdown, Bell's improving performances at parkrun encouraged her to head back to the track and see just what she could achieve.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tentative return\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"lockdown\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell's improving performances\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"parkrun\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'For me and my story, parkrun has featured in so many periods.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my story\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"parkrun\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"so many periods\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been there when I have been flying and feeling really good and when I have had moments that triggered me to say \\\"I want to get back into elite running\\\" because I have found form and fitness.\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"elite\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parkrun was a really good measure of that,' Bell toldMetro.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkrun\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good measure\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell toldMetro\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year Metro has partnered with the iconic charity parkrun to bring you a thriving new content series.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic charity parkrun\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"a thriving new content series\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a coming together of two game-changing powerhouses, Metro has been chosen as the first official media partner for parkrun as it celebrates its 20th birthday in 2024.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two game-changing powerhouses\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"the first official media partner\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"parkrun\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"its 20th birthday\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser thatsupports HTML5 video Up Next It's not just for the runners, though - it's for everyone.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 1.5015628183766044e-11, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2099120974131579e-12, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"a web browser\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"the runners\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Come with us as we embark on a series of boundary-pushing wellbeing content designed to elevate and champion, but also to support mental health and societal cohesion.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"boundary-pushing wellbeing content\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"societal cohesion\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether you run,