my story\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parkrun's origins are in Bushy Park, where the first event featured 13 runners on October 2, 2004.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parkrun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Parkrun\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parkrun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parkrun\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bushy_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.52629350711011e-20, \"text\": \"Bushy Park\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bushy_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bushy_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first event\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"13 runners\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then it has grown into a worldwide phenomenon.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a worldwide phenomenon\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As parkrun marks its 20th birthday this week, Bell acknowledges the importance it plays in so many lives, having run it many times herself.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parkrun\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"its 20th birthday\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2723}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"so many lives\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's something that is so good for the UK.\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9849300752636468, \"rank\": 0.014659485824968657, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know it's international but I feel there is a very British vibe to it having originated in the UK,' said the athlete, who is trained by husband-and-wife duo Trevor Painter and Jenny Meadows.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9996866812580746, \"rank\": 0.00020034132452064735, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9849300752636468, \"rank\": 0.014659485824968657, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3036, \"end\": 3049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Meadows\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"husband-and-wife duo Trevor Painter\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joining parkrun is free - it does not matter if you are a keen runner, a jogger, a walker, a social stroller or are keen to volunteer and cheer from the sidelines.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Joining parkrun\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"a keen runner\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3121}, {\"ngram\": \"a jogger\", \"from\": 3123, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"a walker\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"a social stroller\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3160}, {\"ngram\": \"the sidelines\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Register for parkrun here.\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"parkrun\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did we mention it's free (tick) and you only need to do it once (tick tick).\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"free (tick\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I love the way you see everyone from all age groups - boys, girls, kids, people with dogs, people with babies - and I feel it has such a nice feeling of community, from the volunteers who are giving up their time and are so happy and upbeat, cheering you on, so you get a real feelgood feeling from it plus of course the fact it's free and accessible to anyone.\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3331, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"all age groups\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3375}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"dogs\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3421}, {\"ngram\": \"babies\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3433}, {\"ngram\": \"such a nice feeling\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3473}, {\"ngram\": \"community\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"the volunteers\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3507}, {\"ngram\": \"their time\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3536}, {\"ngram\": \"a real feelgood\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3609}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3640}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The main thing is, which I really believe, is it does not matter which level you are - you are racing against yourself and although it's nice to win, it really does not matter.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main thing\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"which level\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'All the people I know who do parkrun just look for improvement.\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the people\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3881}, {\"ngram\": \"improvement\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My dad will say \\\"this is my fastest time\\\" or \\\"I am this much quicker than last week\\\".\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My dad\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3937}, {\"ngram\": \"my fastest time\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3971}, {\"ngram\": \"last week\", \"from\": 4005, \"to\": 4014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's such a simple idea and has had an incredible impact on people.\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a simple idea\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4040}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible impact\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4073}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Seb Coe did our local one, Kelly Holmes I have seen too.\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4087, \"end\": 4094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seb Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our local one\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4112}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Christmas Day, we will usually get four of us from the family doing it and we will always wear something Christmassy.\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Christmas Day\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4192}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 4198, \"to\": 4208}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"Christmassy\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christmas Day parkrun is a really nice start to the day.'\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Christmas Day parkrun\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4286}, {\"ngram\": \"a really nice start\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4309}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell will follow her successwith marriage to fiance George this month before returning to full training ahead of the 2025 world championships.\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"her successwith marriage\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4365}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4382}, {\"ngram\": \"full training\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4427}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2025 world championships\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has now quit her job to focus fully on athletics, adding: 'I was juggling the full-time job in software sales, which was pretty demanding.\", \"from\": 4468, \"to\": 4610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her job\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4492}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"the full-time job\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4563}, {\"ngram\": \"software sales\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Being able to go full-time with running is an adjustment.\", \"fr